item.title: Hello World! ☕️
item.description: Hello! This is going to be my own personal blog where I can just muse a bit… I’m not really sure what all I’ll be writing about here (or if anyone will even read anything here) but this is mostly for my own amusement, so don’t expect anything amazing. – s
